id: Quán lý vũ khí trang bị Cụm_SLTheoCap

actionConfiguration.body:
SELECT 
    cap_trang_bi,
    COUNT(*) AS so_luong_thiet_bi
FROM 
    public.e_thiet_bi_mang
GROUP BY 
    cap_trang_bi
ORDER BY 
    cap_trang_bi ASC;
